HENRI was raised in a monastery in the Far East where he trained both in martial arts and spiritual study. He seeks to live a life of peace and spiritual serenity but when the sons of a local drug dealer (Eric Roberts) terrorize a small rural town and the police (LaSardo) are powerless to stop them Henri must make a stand.
